                  "content": "Runtime scenarios (repo-evidence):\nS1 Install path: ai-eng install -> templates copy -> hooks install -> state init -> doctor\nS2 Commit path: git add -> ruff format -> lint -> gitleaks -> commit -> push\nS3 PR path: run_commit_workflow -> pre-push checks -> provider PR -> auto-complete\nS4 Gate path: decision-store expiry check -> stack_runner (semgrep/pip-audit/tests/ty)\nS5 Risk path: create decision -> hash context -> expiry/renewal evaluation",
