                  "content": "Dependency inventory (from pyproject + code):\nRuntime: typer, pyyaml, pydantic, keyring, rich\nDev/Gates: pytest, pytest-cov, pytest-xdist, ruff, ty, pip-audit\nSecurity/Gates used in flows: gitleaks, semgrep, pip-audit, sonar checks\nExternal integrations: GitHub CLI/API, Azure DevOps CLI/API, Sonar endpoints",
