                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Operational topology (actual): local CLI + git hooks + repo state + optional CI pipeline.\nNo long-running backend service; reliability depends on local toolchain consistency and hook integrity.",
