                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Suggested measurable SLO set:\n- Gate pass rate >= 95% (rolling 30 days)\n- Hook integrity incidents = 0\n- Mean time to fix broken local readiness < 1 business day\n- Expired risk decisions in active branch = 0",
                  "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                  "fontSize": 12,
